{"title":"煤海春潮","authors":["胡晓"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":3,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤海春潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包头矿务局　胡晓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲响的锣鼓还没放下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又发动起隆隆的马达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛扯大嗓门嚷叫："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山生产新高潮来啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工把北京的春光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装进矿灯撒在井下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百条巷道亮了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪动着跃进的步伐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻头最了解矿工脾气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠劲地钻呀，钻呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮杆紧催着春的种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在煤层里扎根、发芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮声象春雷震荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌子面煤雨哗哗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿车把春光捧到地面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在挥舞冰雪在融化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山那边，烟囱探头瞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，煤海涨潮啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进站的火车欢笑着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把矿工的心意收下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《煤矿工人》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}